title: section 1(2) of the Finance (Tax Appeals and Prospectus Regulation) Act 2019
heading: 2. The 1st day of July 2020 is appointed as the day on which the Finance
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of July 2020 is appointed as the day on which the Finance 
(Tax Appeals and Prospectus Regulation) Act 2019 (No. 39 of 2019) (except 
insofar as it is already in operation) comes into operation. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal of the Minister for Finance, 

30 June, 2020. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 3rd July, 2020.
